        dc:description           "Figure 47. Living snails from Bau A Cyclophorus perdix borneensis (Metcalfe, 1851) ME 8753 Gunung Kapor B Platyrhaphe linita (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 9700 Gunung Doya C Stomacosmethis sadongensis (E. A. Smith, 1895) ME 8761 Gunung Kapor D Pincerna globosa (H. Adams, 1870) ME 8749 Lobang Angin. All not to scale." , "Figure 2. A Chamalycaeus specus (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 9046 Gunung Kapor B Pincerna globosa (H. Adams, 1870) ME 6979 Lobang Angin C Stomacosmethis hosei (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 1010 Gunung Batu D Stomacosmethis sadongensis (E. A. Smith, 1895) ME 8761 Gunung Kapor." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/536835" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/536790" .

